message.body: Oh hey there! Was hoping you didn't misplace my number
I had the paper all weekend in the little pocket on my belt that I designated as the paper pocket. I just got all my digital flotsam back on the grid
Hey I just saw I missed your call. What's up?
I thought i saw an earlier missed call from you.
Oh ha I tried to save you in my phone and don't understand technology and called you
This while being back in the real world thing sucks. Miss pdf
Going back to default is tough, but it feels good to try to inject little bits of the playa into the world.
By the way, congrats on being crowned Miss pdf =p
